.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, begonia, orchid, dahlia, azalea
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, collecting, chess, sudoku, hiking
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the english is the person who growsbellflower
2. the spanish is the owner of the dog
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who growsbegonia
4. the ukranian is the person who's hobby is collecting
5. the person who growsbegonia is to the right of the person who growsorchid
6. the old-gold-smoker is the owner of the snails
7. the kools-smoker is the person who growsdahlia
8. the person who's hobby is chess is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person who's hobby is sudoku
13. the japanese is the parliaments-smoker
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person who growsazalea

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    ukranian	|     english	|    spanish	|    japanese	|
| Flower		|    dahlia	|      azalea	|      bellflower	|     orchid	|     begonia	|
| Hobby	|     hiking	|      collecting	|      chess	| sudoku	|     rock-climbing	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
